.TH LOA-SMART-ADD 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
smart add \- Create or update a smart list
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> smart add
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Prompts for smart list name and filters.
.TP
Filters include read status, location, genre, minimum rating, and required tags.
.TP
If the name exists, the smart list is updated.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> smart add
